{"hash":"ec5e50c96b423917fd23f8317f4a3bf99d08681d","data":{"post":{"title":"Antalya","author":"","date":"2022-10-05","content":"<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221005_132501.jpg\"></p>\n<p>Aangekomen in Antalya. Flink ander landschap!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221005_134149.jpg\"></p>\n<p>Direct maar lunchen.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221005_181540.jpg\"></p>\n<p>Coole straatjes.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221006_082409.jpg\"></p>\n<p>Deze is denk ik niet meer in gebruik.. of toch wel?</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221006_101700.jpg\"></p>\n<p>En we gaan door! Verschillende shots van bezienswaardigheden.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221006_122100.jpg\">\n<img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221006_140903.jpg\">\n<img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221006_135907.jpg\">\n<img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221006_135431.jpg\">\n<img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221006_184805.jpg\"></p>\n<p>Terug naar het hotel. Even relaxen bij het zwembad.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221007_102319.jpg\"></p>\n<p>Nieuwe dag, even de omgeving bekennen en dan richting de Mall!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221007_122025.jpg\">\n<img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221007_132523.jpg\"></p>\n<p>Foodcourt!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221007_153350.jpg\">\n<img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221008_072151.jpg\"></p>\n<p>Op naar de boot, strandje opzoeken.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221008_102252.jpg\">\n<img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221008_104355.jpg\"></p>\n<p>Best wel trots op deze foto.</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221008_125008.jpg\"></p>\n<p>Kan er maar niet aan wennen. Stranden met mini steentjes. Liever zacht zand!</p>\n<p><img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221009_100659.jpg\">\n<img src=\"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221009_113542.jpg\"></p>\n<p>Snel nog een andere Mall bezocht. Klaar om door te gaan naar Istanbul.</p>\n","id":"2ece3ea708db0595e414f89dc2859cef","path":"/blog/turkije-2022/antalya/","image":"https://www.danhnguyen.nl/wp-content/uploads/20221008_072151.jpg","category":{"title":"Goreme, Antalya, Istanbul - Turkije","id":"Goreme, Antalya, Istanbul - Turkije","belongsTo":{"edges":[{"node":{"title":"Goreme","path":"/blog/turkije-2022/goreme/","id":"0d90d76e9aeea8e459ab084f0929dc87","excerpt":"Goreme ook wel bekend voor de 'Insta' luchtbalonnen en mooie landschappen."}},{"node":{"title":"Antalya","path":"/blog/turkije-2022/antalya/","id":"2ece3ea708db0595e414f89dc2859cef","excerpt":"Lekker toerist spelen en genieten van het lekkere weer."}},{"node":{"title":"Istanbul","path":"/blog/turkije-2022/istanbul/","id":"a62793c520acf35e2cfc127c29f10371","excerpt":"Istanbul. Druk."}}]}}}},"context":{}}